metadata.name: RiceCount Journey : Rice Bits
metadata.description:
"beeeeep beeeeep beeeep, new planet is found"

Join the adventure of our rice cooker robot rice bits with mission to discover a new world that need the power of rice. The universe of ricecount is big! will you brave enough to make historice with us?


By Holding this token not only you get this awesome rice cooker robot, it also give access to free mint for future ricecount project. Be a part of our journey because we gonna rice and rise together.
